.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-IMPOSE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
impose \- Impose a PDF for booklet/saddle\-stitch/n\-up printing
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBimpose\fR [\fB\-\-layout\fR] [\fB\-\-paper\fR] [\fB\-\-n\-up\fR] [\fB\-\-signature\fR] [\fB\-\-margins\fR] [\fB\-\-gutter\fR] [\fB\-\-creep\fR] [\fB\-\-crop\-marks\fR] [\fB\-\-duplex\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPDF\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Impose a PDF for booklet/saddle\-stitch/n\-up printing
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-layout\fR \fI<LAYOUT>\fR [default: saddle\-stitch]
Layout: saddle\-stitch, perfect\-bind, n\-up
.TP
\fB\-\-paper\fR \fI<PAPER>\fR [default: a4]
Output paper size
.TP
\fB\-\-n\-up\fR \fI<N_UP>\fR [default: 4]
Pages per sheet (for n\-up; default 4)
.TP
\fB\-\-signature\fR \fI<SIGNATURE>\fR [default: 16]
Pages per signature (for perfect\-bind; default 16)
.TP
\fB\-\-margins\fR \fI<MARGINS>\fR [default: 10]
Margin in mm
.TP
\fB\-\-gutter\fR \fI<GUTTER>\fR [default: 5]
Gutter in mm
.TP
\fB\-\-creep\fR \fI<CREEP>\fR [default: 0]
Creep compensation in mm
.TP
\fB\-\-crop\-marks\fR
Draw crop marks
.TP
\fB\-\-duplex\fR
Add duplex back\-sheet pages
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIPDF\fR>

